query:
UPDATE workspace_diff SET has_changes = true, exists_in_source = $5, exists_in_fork = $6
                    WHERE path = $3 AND kind = $4 AND (
                        (source_workspace_id = $1 AND fork_workspace_id = $2)
                        OR (source_workspace_id = $2 AND fork_workspace_id =$1)
                    )
